<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2023-08-09" class=3D"date-past">09 Aug 2023</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>The MFE UI to get=
 the RAR token from Entitlement engine. This will give a list of&nbsp; acco=
unt IDs to the the Account MFE to use.</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>There is no RAR t=
oken for Feb release.</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2023-10-03" class=3D"date-past">03 Oct 2023</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
<p>ISG approved u<span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">sing Enterprise Vau=
lt to store account IDs</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;"><a href=3D"/download/attachments/=
1460365462/RE%20Technical%20Debt%20-%20ART-5127%20-%20Enterprise%20Vault%20=
