<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false" style=3D"text-align: left;">2</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>Issue</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">CLOSED</spa=
n></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2023-08-10" class=3D"date-past">10 Aug 2023</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Requirement: When the user interac=
ts e.g. getting next page, searching, sorting, the entitlement service (Pin=
g Fed) will give the relevant RAR token/page".</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>The entitlement engine needs to provide search endpoint for the below fi=
elds:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Account number</li>
<li>Account name</li>
<li>Entity name</li>
</ul>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Server-side search, =
sort, and pagination cannot be done without the search functionality from t=
he entitlement engine.</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2023-09-06" class=3D"date-past">06 Sep 2023</time>&nbs=
p;&nbsp;</p>
<p>With the either of the interim solutions mentioned in row #1,&nbsp; we w=
ill not have server-side search and sort for the Feb release.</p>
<p>It could be the client-side search&nbsp; and sort if we decide we want i=
t for Feb.</p>
</div><p>Also, there is no <u>pagination </u>for Feb.</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M059852" =
href=3D"/display/~M059852" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1212885730" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Zane Zuo</a></p>
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M058573" =
href=3D"/display/~M058573" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1125291984" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Ave Cahyadi</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"F072612" =
href=3D"/display/~F072612" data-linked-resource-id=3D"125976272" data-linke=
d-resource-version=3D"2" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-u=
rl=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Andrea For</a>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false" style=3D"text-align: left;">3</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>Issue</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">CLOSED</spa=
n></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2023-10-03" class=3D"date-past">03 Oct 2023</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">10x B2B API authentication method =
is using the API key. However, Mesh authentication methods don't&nbsp; supp=
ort this.&nbsp;</span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">The proxy APIs can't=
 bet set up until there is a change in either of 10x or Mesh</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p style=3D"text-align: left;">We had a meeting with ISG team and all other=
 relevant stakeholders and decided to use fallback plan (dummy basic authen=
tication) for Feb-release, of course with technical debts to be recorded.</=
p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;"><a href=3D"/download/attachments/1460365462/=
RE%20Reconvene%20and%20agree%20on%20Feb%2024%2010x%20Authentication%20Model=
.msg?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1698205960433&amp;api=3Dv2" data-li=
nked-resource-id=3D"1522216195" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-lin=
ked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"RE R=
econvene and agree on Feb 24 10x Authentication Model.msg" data-linked-reso=
urce-content-type=3D"application/vnd.ms-outlook" data-linked-resource-conta=
iner-id=3D"1460365462" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"126">RE Re=
convene and agree on Feb 24 10x Authentication Model.msg</a></p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;">Jira ticket to track the decision:<span>&nbs=
p;</span><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://jira.srv.westpac.com.au=
/browse/ART-7259" style=3D"text-decoration: none;" rel=3D"nofollow">https:/=
/jira.srv.westpac.com.au/browse/ART-7259</a></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M014147" =
href=3D"/display/~M014147" data-linked-resource-id=3D"7267669" data-linked-=
resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=
=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Mark Chan</a>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false" style=3D"text-align: left;">4</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>Assumption</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">CLOSED</spa=
n></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2023-11-27" class=3D"date-past">27 Nov 2023</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Product Versioning and product lif=
ecycle within 10x is restricted to one <em><u>current</u> (latest) </em>ver=
sion.</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">When a Product is amended, a new v=
ersion is generated and all attached subscriptions are migrated on the effe=
ctive date. ie. There is no possibility of a subscription to be set to a no=
n-latest version Product.</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">10x are evaluating future capabili=
ty to allow for concurrent versions of the same Product and this assumption=
 may need to be assessed if that eventuates.</span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Retrieval of Prod=
uct Details in the 10x API returns the latest version of the Product which =
is fit for purpose.</p><p><br></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p style=3D"text-align: left;">None required at this point in time. Should =
this assumption be invalidated with 10x design changes, the layering of the=
 Banking Platform 10x API's will insulate impacts to CCMP.</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M057516" =
href=3D"/display/~M057516" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1049210668" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Unknown User (m057516)</a> <a=
 class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M014147" href=
=3D"/display/~M014147" data-linked-resource-id=3D"7267669" data-linked-reso=
urce-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"=
https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Mark Chan</a> <a class=3D"confluence=
-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M013951" href=3D"/display/~M013951=
" data-linked-resource-id=3D"63929678" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" d=
ata-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"https://confluence.s=
rv.westpac.com.au">Mark Nguyen</a> @Simon Loftus (10x)</p>
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"F069295" =
href=3D"/display/~F069295" data-linked-resource-id=3D"710484085" data-linke=
d-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-u=
rl=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Madalena Chan</a>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
