<h2 id=3D"id-01.SD:AccountListing(10xOnly)-OutofScopeforBeta-Feb*">Out of S=
cope for Beta-Feb*</h2>
<ul>
<li>Viewing a snapshot of accounts, including over a period (Aggregated bal=
ances)</li>
<li>Viewing non-10X accounts</li>
<li>Viewing non-CIA / CTA account</li>
<li><p>Receiving RAR token (no entitlement check)</p></li>
<li>Server-side search, sort, and pagination (entitlement engine)</li>
</ul>
<h2 id=3D"id-01.SD:AccountListing(10xOnly)-UserStoryTraceability"><span>Use=
r Story Traceability</span></h2>
<p>Account Listing (10x) user stories: <a href=3D"/display/ARTC/4366+Detail=
ed+Requirements#id-4366DetailedRequirements-UserStories">4366 Detailed Requ=
irements#UserStories</a></p>
<h3 id=3D"id-01.SD:AccountListing(10xOnly)-Non-FunctionalRequirementsTracea=
bility">Non-Functional Requirements Traceability</h3>
<p>Non-functional requirements: <a href=3D"/display/ARTC/Non-Functional+Req=
uirements+-+Channels+Squad+NFRs">Non-Functional Requirements - Channels Squ=
ad NFRs</a></p>
<h3 id=3D"id-01.SD:AccountListing(10xOnly)-Constraints&amp;Dependencies">Co=
nstraints &amp; Dependencies</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 364.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 372.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 480.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 361.0px;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 184.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Ref #</st=
rong></p><p>[A-###, C-###, D-###]</p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Considera=
tions Type</strong></p><p>[Assumptions, Constraints, Dependencies]</p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Descripti=
on</strong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Notes</st=
rong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Date</str=
ong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>C-001</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Constraint</p></t=
d>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span>10x's accou=
nt search endpoint (<a href=3D"https://docs.10xbanking.com/b2c/reference/se=
archsubscriptions" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">POST &nbsp;/v3/=
subscriptions/search</a>) currently can serve only 1<u> account at each cal=
l</u>. So the service layer should handle any required loop.</span></p><p><=
span>This wouldn't impact account MFE performance much as the list of the a=
ccounts is limited for Feb release. However, it will impact the performance=
 as the number of accounts increase.</span></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>We need to raise an NFR with 10x for <u>post Feb</u> as we will have mor=
e accounts in each call that can impact the performance.</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>C-002</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Constraint</p></t=
d>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>&nbsp;The endpoin=
t <strong>POST /arrangements/search</strong> in the <u>Arrangement Customer=
 API</u> (inf-bnkng-arrngmnt-arrngmntpartyrole-arrngmntcust-v2)&nbsp; accep=
ts one account number + BSB at a time. It needs to uplifted to accept an ar=
ray of account numbers and BSBs.</p><p><br></p><p>There is another endpoint=
, POST /arrangements, which accepts an array. But it also requires having t=
he <u>CPC</u>, where as CCMP Arrangements CAP API doesn't have to it to pro=
vide.</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a href=3D"/download/attachments/1460365462/Potentially%20a%20new%20reso=
urce%20for%20the%20arrangement%20api%20from%20CCMP.msg?version=3D1&amp;modi=
ficationDate=3D1696284580970&amp;api=3Dv2" data-linked-resource-id=3D"15040=
64881" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"atta=
chment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"Potentially a new resource fo=
r the arrangement api from CCMP.msg" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"a=
pplication/vnd.ms-outlook" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1460365462"=
 data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"126">Potentially a new resource =
for the arrangement api from CCMP.msg</a></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h1 id=3D"id-01.SD:AccountListing(10xOnly)-TechnicalDebt">Technical Debt</h=
1>
