<p><strong>See the details here: <a class=3D"" href=3D"https://confluence.s=
rv.westpac.com.au/x/kBF1X" rel=3D"nofollow">https://confluence.srv.westpac.=
com.au/x/kBF1X</a></strong></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-01.SD:AccountListing(10xOnly)-SecurityAspects">Security Aspect=
s</h2>
<p>The Galaxy application security is per below.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Authentication</strong>: It will be handled with Ping Federate =
using PKCE flow.</li>
<li><strong>Authorisation</strong>: List of account IDs that the user is en=
titled to see using the interim solution that is yet to be approved by ISG.=
</li>
</ul>
