<h2 id=3D"id-01.SD:AccountListing(10xOnly)-ErrorHandling">Error Handling</h=
2>
<h3 id=3D"id-01.SD:AccountListing(10xOnly)-Summary:">Summary:</h3>
<p>For Feb-release, the below error codes should be handled by the UI:</p>
<ul>
<li>Bad Request Error</li>
<li>Server Error</li>
<li>Timeout Error</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Read more here: <a class=3D"" href=3D"https://confluence.srv.wes=
tpac.com.au/x/TDumWQ" rel=3D"nofollow">https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.a=
u/x/TDumWQ</a></strong></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-01.SD:AccountListing(10xOnly)-Data&amp;InformationModel">Data =
&amp; Information Model&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>
<p>All mappings between UI and each service layer listed in below.</p>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">Account UI-Experience API Mappin=
g: <a class=3D"" href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/Syj3Vw" re=
l=3D"nofollow">https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/Syj3Vw</a></span></l=
i>
<li>Account Experience API- Source Systems Data Mapping: <a class=3D"" href=
=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/g87_Vw" rel=3D"nofollow">https:=
//confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/g87_Vw</a></li>
<li>W1C Arrangements CAP API- Source Systems Data Mapping: <a class=3D"" hr=
ef=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/R2jeW" rel=3D"nofollow">https=
://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/R2jeW</a></li>
<li>10x Accounts CAP API- Source Systems Data Mapping: <a class=3D"" href=
