<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false" style=3D"text-align: left;">3</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Develop API;</p>
<ul>
<li>Learn more Mesh API development here: <a class=3D"" href=3D"https://con=
fluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/zZa4Rw" rel=3D"nofollow">h</a><a class=3D"" hr=
ef=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/65a4Rw" rel=3D"nofollow">http=
s://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/65a4Rw</a></li>
<li>Reference to Java development (last update in 2017): <a class=3D"" href=
=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/GkWaAg" rel=3D"nofollow">https:=
//confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/GkWaAg</a></li>
<li>Learn about Mesh runtime profiles (Java web, Boot Spring, etc.) here: <=
a class=3D"" href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/SUGXOw" rel=3D=
"nofollow">https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/SUGXOw</a></li>
<li>Learn more about testing and mocking here: <a class=3D"" href=3D"https:=
//confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/FdFjUw" rel=3D"nofollow">https://confluen=
ce.srv.westpac.com.au/x/FdFjUw</a></li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Account engineering =
team</td>
